Package org.apache.wicket.examples.hangman

Class Summary
Game Implementation of the actual hangman game model.
Guess The main guess page for the hangman application.
HangmanApplication Class defining the main Game application.
HangmanPage Session for hangman game.
HangmanSession Session for hangman game.
Home The home page for the hangman application.
Letter Model for a letter in the game of hangman
Lose Page that handles the loser failing to guess the word.
Win Page called when the user has correctly guessed the word.
Word Model for a word in the game of Game.
WordGenerator The word generator is responsible for reading in a list of words from a data file and serving them up in a random order.
